t Party (Pre-1996).svg|size=21px}} [[Peng Dehuai]]\n* {{Flagdeco|United States|1912|size=23px}} [[Joseph Stilwell]]\n* {{Flagdeco|United States|1912|size=23px}} [[Claire Chennault]]\n* {{Flagdeco|Soviet Union|1936|size=23px}} [[Vasily Chuikov]]}}\n| commander2 = {{plainlist|\n* {{Flagicon image|Flag of the Japanese Emperor.svg|size=30px}} '''[[Hirohito]]'''<br><small>([[Emperor of Japan]])</small>\n* {{Flagdeco|Empire of Japan|army|size=23px}} [[Shunroku Hata]]\n* {{Flagdeco|Empire of Japan|army|size=23px}} [[Yasuji Okamura]]\n* {{Flagdeco|Empire of Japan|army|size=23px}} [[Prince Kan'in Kotohito|Kotohito Kan'in]]\n* {{Flagdeco|Empire of Japan|army|size=23px}} [[Hajime Sugiyama]]\n* {{Flagdeco|Empire of Japan|army|size=23px}} [[Toshiz\u014d Nishio]]\n* {{Flagdeco|Empire of Japan|army|size=23px}} [[Hisaichi Terauchi]]\n* {{Flagdeco|Empire of Japan|army|size=23px}} [[Hayao Tada]]\n* {{Flagdeco|Empire of Japan|army|size=23px}} [[Iwane Matsui]]\n* {{Flagdeco|Empire of Japan|army|size=23px}} [[Yasuhiko Asaka]]\n* {{Flagdeco|Empire of Japan|army|size=23px}} [[Seishir\u014d Itagaki]]\n* {{Flagdeco|Empire of Japan|army|size=23px}} [[Hideki T\u014dj\u014d]]\n* {{Flagdeco|Empire of Japan|army|size=23px}} [[Yoshijir\u014d Umezu]]\n* {{Flagdeco|Empire of Japan|army|size=23px}} [[Naozaburo Okabe]]\n* {{Flagdeco|Manchukuo}} [[Puyi]]\n* {{flagdeco|Mengjiang}} [[Demchugdongrub]]\n* [[File:Flag of the Republic of China-Nanjing (Peace, National Construction).svg|23px]] [[Wang Jingwei]]\n* [[File:Flag of the Republic of China-Nanjing (Peace, National Construction).svg|23px]] [[Chen Gongbo]]\n}}\n| strength1 = {{plainlist|\n* {{Flagicon image|Naval_Jack_of_the_Republic_of_China.svg}} '''Chinese Nationalists''' (including [[Warlord era|regional warlords]]):\n** 1,700,000 (1937)<ref>[http://ww2-weapons.com/chinese-nationalist-army/ The Chinese Nationalist Army, ww2-weapons.com] Retrieved 11 March 2016</ref>\n** 2,600,000 (1939)<ref name=\"Hsiung 171\">Hsiung, ''China's Bitter Victory'', 